Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.25,0:00:25.67,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\be3}駆け抜けるダンジョンsea of trees
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.33,0:00:28.63,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\be3}let's get ready to rumble, we can go
