Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.01,0:00:39.76,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\be3}Aiya iya
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.76,0:00:40.93,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\be3}很好…一起開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.18,0:00:42.35,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\be3}是時候飛翔了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.35,0:00:43.48,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\be3}我要死在興奮之中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.48,0:00:44.56,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\be3}什麼都不在乎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.56,0:00:45.35,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\be3}你的身體已經行動
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.35,0:00:46.85,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\be3}照向地下的光
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.85,0:00:48.02,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\be3}他如此蠻不講理
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.02,0:00:49.31,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\be3}我們的夢已渺茫…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.31,0:00:54.19,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\be3}可我們依舊戰鬥 究竟是為誰？
